data.description: Welcome home to 3705 Springbrook Ln! This 4 bed, 2.5 bath, 2 story home is situated in the desirable Ravenswood neighborhood of Lansing, MI. The main level of this home consists of the living, dining, kitchen and great room along with Cali bamboo flooring. The kitchen features updated countertops, cabinets, and a beautiful marble tiling. Upstairs you'll find 4 bedrooms along with 2 full baths! Downstairs, a full basement offers plenty of room for storage and is ready to be finished as you wish!Outside, a large deck just off the dining area overlooks the partially fenced in backyard. Additional features include: an attached 2 car garage and central air! Seller reserves: refrigerator, dishwasher, washer, dryer, TV & mounts, and all curtains & rods.
